m/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-last-of-us-developer-naughty-dog-laying-off-contractors-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-last-of-us-developer-naughty-dog-laying-off-contractors-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-last-of-us-developer-naughty-dog-laying-off-contractors-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-last-of-us-developer-naughty-dog-laying-off-contractors-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-last-of-us-developer-naughty-dog-laying-off-contractors-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-last-of-us"><em>《最后生还者》</em></a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/uncharted"><em>《神秘海域》</em></a>系列的开发商<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/naughty-dog">顽皮狗</a>据称已经缩短了一些员工合同，作为裁员计划的一部分。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/best-upcoming-games-we-saw-at-gamescom-2023-3505950">以下是我们在 Gamescom 2023 上看到的一些即将推出的最佳游戏</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://kotaku.com/naughty-dog-ps5-playstation-sony-last-us-part-3-layoffs-1850893794"><em>Kotaku</em></a>报道称，有两名消息人士联系了该刊物，询问艺术、制作和质量保证等一系列部门的裁员情况。</p><p>顽皮狗的全职员工和开发人员似乎没有被包括在这些裁员中，他们声称“至少 25 名开发人员”受到了影响。</p><p>显然，受影响的人将被要求在整个十月份工作，因为他们的合同将在本月底正式终止。此外， <em>Kotaku</em>的消息人士称，员工们感到“压力”，不允许公众得知这一消息。 </p><figure id="attachment_3342073" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3342073" style="width: 696px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3342073" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/The-Last-of-Us-2-Best-PS4-Games@2000x1270-696x442-1.jpg" alt="《最后生还者 第二部》预览图" width="696" height="442" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/The-Last-of-Us-2-Best-PS4-Games@2000x1270-696x442-1.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/The-Last-of-Us-2-Best-PS4-Games@2000x1270-696x442-1-400x254.jpg 400w" sizes="(max-width: 696px) 100vw, 696px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3342073" class="wp-caption-text"> 《最后生还者第二部分》。图片来源：顽皮狗</figcaption></figure><p>最后，对于不再为 Naughty Dog 工作的 25 名开发人员，公司不会提供遣散费。当<em>Kotaku</em>联系索尼时，索尼没有发表评论，截至撰写本文时，开发商或发行商也没有发表任何声明。</p><p>尽管一些主要参与者取得了成功，但今年工作室的裁员却出现了前所未有的激增。<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/electronic-arts">艺电</a>首席执行官安德鲁·威尔逊 (Andrew Wilson) 宣布，该公司<a href="https://www.ea.com/news/electronic-arts-reports-q1-fy24-financial-results?isLocalized=true">2024 财年第一季度的净预订量同比增长 21%，创下“创纪录的第一季度”</a> 。</p><p>然而， <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/immortals-of-aveum"><em>Immortals Of Aveum</em></a>开发商 Ascendant Studios <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/immortals-of-aveum-developer-loses-45-per-cent-of-staff-due-to-poor-sales-3498537">被迫裁员近一半</a>。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/ascendant-studios">Ascendant Studios</a>隶属于美国艺电公司 (Electronic Arts)，由曾参与<em>《使命召唤》</em>和<em>《死亡空间》的开发人员组成。</em></p><p>据称， <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/team17">Team17</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/team17-to-reportedly-make-tens-of-redundancies-this-month-3507780?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=team17-to-reportedly-make-tens-of-redundancies-this-month">在本月给员工的一封内部信中还计划削减“数十名员工”</a> 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3418766" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3418766" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3418766" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Dredge-2-credit-Black-Salt-Games@2000x1270.jpg" alt="疏通" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Dredge-2-credit-Black-Salt-Games@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Dredge-2-credit-Black-Salt-Games@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Dredge-2-credit-Black-Salt-Games@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Dredge-2-credit-Black-Salt-Games@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Dredge-2-credit-Black-Salt-Games@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Dredge-2-credit-Black-Salt-Games@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3418766" class="wp-caption-text"> “挖泥机”信用：Team17</figcaption></figure><p> “正如今天的公告中所解释的，我们刚刚公布了半年业绩，显示集团上半年实现了强劲增长，”集团首席执行官安·赫尔利 (Ann Hurley) 对员工表示。</p><p> “然而，我们认识到这些结果是在行业有史以来高质量产品发布和同行大幅折扣竞争最激烈的年份之一的背景下实现的，”她继续说道。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，作为对反垄断指控进行更广泛调查的一部分<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/nvidia-offices-raided-by-french-authorities-in-anti-trust-investigation-3507608">，英伟达的法国办事处遭到警方突击搜查</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-last-of-us-developer-is-the-latest-studio-to-be-hit-with-layoffs-3508507">《最后生还者》开发商是最新一家遭遇裁员的工作室的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 《权力的游戏》演员约瑟夫·盖特因儿童性犯罪指控出庭https://www.nme.com/news/tv/game-of-thrones-actor-joseph-gatt-appears-court-child-sex-offence-charge-3508533?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=game-of- 《权力的游戏》演员约瑟夫·盖特因儿童性犯罪指控出庭Adam StarkeyTue, 03 Oct 2023 15:09:20 +0000 NewsTV News https://www.nme.com/?p=3508533 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Joseph-Gatt-main.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="约瑟夫·盖特" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Joseph-Gatt-main.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Joseph-Gatt-main-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Joseph-Gatt-main-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Joseph-Gatt-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Joseph-Gatt-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Joseph-Gatt-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>盖特去年四月因涉嫌向未成年人发送露骨色情信息而被捕</p><p>《<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">权力</a><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/game-of-thrones-actor-joseph-gatt-appears-court-child-sex-offence-charge-3508533">的游戏》演员约瑟夫·加特 (Joseph Gatt) 因儿童性犯罪指控出庭受审</a></p>; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Joseph-Gatt-main.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="约瑟夫·盖特" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Joseph-Gatt-main.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Joseph-Gatt-main-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Joseph-Gatt-main-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Joseph-Gatt-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Joseph-Gatt-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Joseph-Gatt-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/game-of-thrones"><em>《权力的游戏》</em></a>演员约瑟夫·加特在被指控向未成年人发送露骨的性信息后出庭。</p><p>这位在<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/hbo">HBO</a>剧集中扮演 Thenn Warg 的演员被拍到周一（10 月 2 日）与女友 Mercy Malick 一起抵达洛杉矶法庭。</p><p>盖特于 2022 年 4 月因性犯罪指控被捕，目前还面临第二项持有攻击性武器重罪指控。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-12585697/Game-Thrones-Joseph-Gatt-court-child-sex-offense.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《每日邮报》</em></a>报道，洛杉矶高等法院法官 Enrique Monguia 表示，在检察官 Michael Fern 表示“需要更多证据”才能推进案件后，听证会将于 12 月 4 日继续进行。 </p><figure id="attachment_3508560" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3508560" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3508560" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Joseph-Gatt-new.jpg" alt="约瑟夫·盖特" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Joseph-Gatt-new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Joseph-Gatt-new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Joseph-Gatt-new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Joseph-Gatt-new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Joseph-Gatt-new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Joseph-Gatt-new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3508560" class="wp-caption-text">约瑟夫·盖特于去年四月被捕。图片来源：Paul Archuleta/FilmMagic</figcaption></figure><p>洛杉矶警察局收到消息称盖特“与一名未成年人跨州进行网上色情交流”后，盖特被捕。</p><p>他位于比佛利山庄的家随后被针对儿童网络犯罪（ICAC）工作组青少年部门的警察搜查。</p><p>盖特对两项指控均表示不认罪，18 个月前被捕后，他缴纳了 5,000 美元（4,138 英镑）的保释金，目前仍可保释。</p><p>这位演员被捕一周后在推特上否认了这些指控，他写道：“我显然想解决最近针对我提出的绝对令人震惊和完全不真实的指控。</p><p> “他们百分百绝对错误且鲁莽。我已确认今天的新闻稿中存在错误和误导性信息。我正在全力配合警方和洛杉矶警察局查明此事的真相。我期待着洗清自己的名声。”</p><p>除了<em>《权力的游戏》</em>之外，盖特还出现在电影<em>《雷神》</em> 、 <em>《星际迷航：暗黑无界》</em>和蒂姆·伯顿 2019 年翻拍的真人版《<em>小飞象</em>》中。</p